            "title": "盤中速報 - 聯茂(6213)股價拉至漲停，漲停價216.5元，成交14,920張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯茂(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6213:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6213\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6213-TW</a>)09日09:19上漲19.5元，股價漲停報216.5元，委買23張、委賣1,698張，成交14,920張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為多層印刷電路基材及銅箔基板及半成品及成品之製造、加工及買賣。電子零組件製造業。電子材料批發業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯茂(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6213:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6213\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6213-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲20.86%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲4.78%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-2,273 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-6,725 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+2,463 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+1,989 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,816 張</li> <li>融券增減：+266 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
