            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台虹(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8039:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8039\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8039-TW</a>)09日09:19股價上漲9元，報133.0元，漲幅7.26%，成交9,257張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台虹(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8039:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8039\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8039-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為高分子薄膜銅箔積層板。保護膠片。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲11.71%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲4.78%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,782 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,154 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+160 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+468 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,271 張</li> <li>融券增減：+146 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
